{"title":"Professor Yozo Yokota (1940-2019)","link":"https://iafor.org/professor-yozo-yokota-1940-2019/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=professor-yozo-yokota-1940-2019","date":1561080678000,"content":"<p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Professor-Yozo-Yokota-1940-2019-150x150.jpg\" srcset=\"https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Professor-Yozo-Yokota-1940-2019-150x150.jpg 150w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Professor-Yozo-Yokota-1940-2019-600x600.jpg 600w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Professor-Yozo-Yokota-1940-2019-100x100.jpg 100w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Professor-Yozo-Yokota-1940-2019-50x50.jpg 50w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Professor-Yozo-Yokota-1940-2019-300x300.jpg 300w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Professor-Yozo-Yokota-1940-2019-32x32.jpg 32w\" />IAFOR members were saddened to learn of the passing of Professor Yozo Yokota on June 12, 2019. Professor Yokota was an international champion of human rights, a legal giant in Japan, and a friend to many throughout the IAFOR network. Yokota served as the UN’s Special Rapporteur to Myanmar investigating the human rights’ situation there <a href=\"https://iafor.org/professor-yozo-yokota-1940-2019/\">...</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://iafor.org/professor-yozo-yokota-1940-2019/\">Professor Yozo Yokota (1940-2019)</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://iafor.org\">The International Academic Forum (IAFOR)</a>.</p>","author":"IAFOR","siteTitle":"The International Academic Forum (IAFOR)","siteHash":"db6175d8277e1d8dd86d5cc607b1dd9335cce255aa7e00b46d0931f23a0d47f6","entryHash":"1ffb643df3672713d1af523af5950e0b1855812a9dd3c5e92cdeb00fc1d60263","category":"Interdisciplinary"}